\begin_layout Subsubsection
Performance mining
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Process performance mining consists on extracting process execution performance
 in an aggregate or detailed level.
 There are different techniques that can be used:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Duration-enhanced process maps.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Duration-enhanced BPMN models.
